metadata.name: AQUA
metadata.description:
If ever there is magic on the earth, it is contained in water. 

The term aqua in latin means "water" or "the sea". This image takes you on a visual exploration as the calm waters mix with the sands from below.

The result is a remarkable barrel of textures formed to create this beautiful aqua setting. 

This is a 1/1 edition with a high resolution image included to accompany the NFT. 

3358 x 4408 px
